name: warmup-async
description: ## Setup * Work in a repository for this warmup exercise (`warmup-async`)   * On each day, create a new folder and branch of this repo with the date     * i.e. `YYYY-MM-DD`   * Submit a PR from that branch to your master for review   * If you are deploying to Heroku or Code Sandbox, provide that link as well   * Timebox this to 1 hour
